{"tid":859103,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★19歲失業男欠財仔逾10萬危站天台","createTime":"2018-10-12T09:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T13:39:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b01278058d1c2f9303ea1a0a4bb453b1450ae4","tid":859103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/photo/bkn-20181012005948021-1012_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181012103150\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181012%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181012005948021-1012_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181012103150&h=c8737ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青年大角咀企圖跳樓獲救。今日(12日)凌晨零時許，警方接獲一名年姓麥(19歲)青年報案，指他於中匯街48-58號中耀樓16樓天台圖跳樓輕生。西九龍總區衝鋒隊聞訊趕至現場，登上天台查看，終尋獲事主，經大約1小時游說將事主勸服，由救護車送院。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，麥曾任職清潔工，疑因欠下財務公司約10萬元債項、而且近日失業、加上牽涉刑事案件致情緒低落。西九龍總區衝鋒隊第2隊李永業高級督察表示，當他與數名同袍抵達上址，發現一名青年危站壆邊。經初步了解，得知他受多個問題困擾自尋短見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012005948021-1012_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181012%2Fbkn-20181012005948021-1012_00822_001.html&d=SOIlvL8gMyq5cs67G5zfIzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=532a67c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012005948021-1012_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce13d2535c4d80b0e65d0019f20cdd5e6cff8596","tid":859103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"700 or 175"},{"pid":"aff37ff9f8b5cdd41ce828e1ffc0038c30f28ea6","tid":859103,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"49000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1709146abfe9f3f0bc69c3c082067d522d1e06c2","tid":859103,"uid":125488,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"19歲差果10萬就跳樓？<br